    %h2 Professional Promotion
    %p
      There are a lot of professional advertisers. For sure they can promote your ecommerce business up to sky. You have web pages with your storefront and products. They can rise high traffic to theese pages. 
      %br 
      If you don't know how to start - look at Facebook App Advertisement. We had very good experience with this advertising platform. You can adjust geography location and demographics of audience for your ads.

.row
  .col-xs-12.col-sm-4
    = image_tag "upward-graph.jpg", class: 'img-responsive img-center img-padding-top'
  .col-xs-12.col-sm-8
    %h2 Inbound Marketing
    %p
      Another terrific source for promotion is Inbound Marketing - embedded feature of Androcommerce free plan. Simply put this is blog injected into your storefront app. You can decorate your sales into mentorship in your area. You can put announcements of world-class events, photos of new products, reviews and head-to-head comparisons of brand new products, or just discount coupons in your shop. This information will be immediately delivered to all installed storefront apps via Push Notifications. So you will be in touch with your customers and they will follow you as an expert and local leader in direction parallel.

